{"tag":{"label":"2024","permalink":"/garden/tags/2024","allTagsPath":"/garden/tags","count":16,"items":[{"id":"diary/2024/0718/0718","title":"0718","description":"這幾天的自己和世界像是隔了一層膜，這裡的空氣稀薄、水位高漲，外邊則是閃閃亮亮喧喧鬧鬧，但隔著膜我看不清也聽不懂那些愉悅。","permalink":"/garden/diary/2024/0718/"},{"id":"diary/2024/0719","title":"0720","description":"多眠．頭痛","permalink":"/garden/diary/2024/0719"},{"id":"diary/2024/0813","title":"0813","description":"Shut down","permalink":"/garden/diary/2024/0813"},{"id":"diary/2024/1103","title":"1103","description":"睡眠問題從大學的某個時刻開始就斷斷續續地困擾著我，最近失眠得比較嚴重，寫這篇文的當下如是。在大半夜的時候總是會比較 Emo，反正也睡不著，不如就起身來面對並寫寫仍不時困住我的這些東西吧。","permalink":"/garden/diary/2024/1103"},{"id":"product-notes/Heptabase/observing002/observing002","title":"1st AMA 讀後感","description":"Heptabase AMA 2024/08","permalink":"/garden/product-notes/Heptabase/observing002/"},{"id":"tech-notes/AI/AI-limitation/AI-limitation","title":"AI 的先天限制","description":"即使 AI 的發展越來越進步，它依然面臨一些先天性的限制，讓它在實際應用中可能產生誤差或不準確的情況。","permalink":"/garden/tech-notes/AI/AI-limitation/"},{"id":"tech-notes/AI/LLM/LLM","title":"LLM 是 AI 的一個子集合","description":"近年迅速竄起的 AI 產業風潮，精確來說是由使用大型語言模型（Large language model, LLM）技術的工具所引領，而 LLM 是人工智慧（Artificial Intelligence, AI）的一個子集。","permalink":"/garden/tech-notes/AI/LLM/"},{"id":"tech-notes/AI/prompt-engineering/prompt-engineering","title":"Prompting 技巧","description":"在使用 LLM 時，提示語（Prompt）的撰寫方式會直接影響 AI 回應的品質，因此初步理解提示工程（Prompt engineering）這門用來設計與撰寫指令的技術，能夠幫助自己引導 AI 提供更有用、清晰、並且符合需求的結果。","permalink":"/garden/tech-notes/AI/prompt-engineering/"},{"id":"website-notes/rss-to-email/rss-to-email","title":"RSS to Email： RSS 更新即寄 Email","description":"subscribe","permalink":"/garden/website-notes/rss-to-email/"},{"id":"t-t-changelog/v1.0.0/v1.0.0","title":"v1.0.0","description":"Release date: 2024/07/04","permalink":"/garden/t-t-changelog/v1.0.0/"},{"id":"t-t-changelog/v1.1.0/v1.1.0","title":"v1.1.0","description":"Release date: 2024/07/17","permalink":"/garden/t-t-changelog/v1.1.0/"},{"id":"t-t-changelog/v1.2.0/v1.2